::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' Lady Serval... My Lady Serval...
::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' ...
::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' {{Size|36|...Who are you!?}}
::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' Ah! I know...
::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' You are a loyal servant of Lady Serval. You've come to admire her radiant beauty, right?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} It's true. I am her fan.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404012533-->
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' Ah! I never imagined to meet another fan here...
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' ...especially someone like me who enjoys climbing onto the workshop window to see Lady Serval's beautiful face up close all day long without any obstructions!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm a Silvermane Guard, responding to a report.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404012536-->
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' N&mdash;No way. You aren't even in uniform! I've never seen a Silvermane Guard who walks around during the day in weird clothes.
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' You must be a fan just like me...
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' ...someone like me who enjoys climbing onto the workshop window to see Lady Serval's beautiful face up close all day long without any obstructions!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_404012539-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404012539-->
::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' So... You strike me as a bold person. Can I ask you for a favor?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Umm. I think you've got the wrong impression...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404012541-->
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' Wrong impression? There are no wrong impressions between the fans of Lady Serval!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} How can you tell?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404012543-->
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' Fans who enjoy Lady Serval all have pretty good discernment!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You're not about to ask me to go take her picture, are you...?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404012545-->
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' You're so smart! Just what I'd expect from a fellow fan of Lady Serval!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_404012546-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404012546-->
::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' In fact... I was just about to ask if you could help take a picture of Lady Serval!
::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' Is that alright?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Leave it to me.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404012549-->
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' My goodness! You really are a good person!
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' So... I'll leave that to your capable hands!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} This goes against public order and common decency...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404012552-->
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' My goodness! You really are a good person!
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' Don't worry! Taking a picture of Lady Serval is just another form of Preservation!
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' ...Probably! Please handle this for me!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_404012555-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404012555-->
::'''(Trailblazer):''' (Should I help her?)
::'''(Trailblazer):''' (Or maybe... go and tell Serval?)
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
