::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' You... Y&mdash;You...
::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' You took Lady Serval's... picture!?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Here you go.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404012634-->
:;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Finish: 404012605-->)
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' Ah...
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' Ah...
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' {{Size|36|Ah! The face!}}
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' {{Size|36|Ah! The nose!}}
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' {{Size|36|Ah! The eyes!}}
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' Lady Serval truly is... just too perfect! She's as beautiful as the Supreme Guardian...
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' I'm so lucky to be alive now! I've had the opportunity to see something so perfect!
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' Save me! I think... Lady Serval has caused my heart to skip several beats... I want to hang Lady Serval's picture on my headboard... That way I can see her every day!
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' Until we meet again, my fellow fan! I need to go and recover... I hope that the next time we meet...
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' {{Size|36|We all can have a new picture of Lady Serval!}}
