:::The girl in front of you takes a breath of air in an exaggerated pose.
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' Hurry... Hurry up and show me!
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' Huh? Where is my beloved Lady Serval?
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Sorry, I didn't get her in the picture.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404012638-->
