::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404012640-->
::::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' Oh... Then it must be because I'm not smart enough.
::::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' I'm not worthy of Lady Serval's genius!
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_404012642-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404012642-->
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' But... that's OK! I can keep seeing her up close like this. Lady Serval, she's as beautiful as a flower...
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' Until we meet again, my fellow fan! I hope that the next time we meet...
:::'''Serval's Fanatic Fan:''' {{Size|36|We all can have a picture of Lady Serval!}}
